* Biomass continued towards the IF, seeing with his scanners that his strike 
had had a very pleasing effect on Perndabot and his balence.
Little did he know but it was his adranalin rising that was making this as 
pleasing as it was, liking to test his power against a bigger foe like this.
But he stops when he hears the click of a fully loaded missil launched aimed 
at the back of his skull, chuckling to himself as he looks over his shoulder 
at Perndabot.*

" Sensative about your sex, hmm?"

* Biomass turns around so that he was looking along the line of his shoulder 
towards Perndabot, a smile on his face but one that was more wicked then 
happy.
Without hesitation he walks back towards Perndabot, moving so that the end 
of the missil launched was pressed up against his chest-plate. His nose 
inches awat from Perndabots.*

" I thought you women were proud to be what you are?"

* Nue'e glared at both of them, stepping back and rolling her eyes while 
pushing her glasses up.
This was stupid.*
